<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-30-0059 </DOCNO><TEXT>The following explanations deal with standard setting in the environmentallaws of the USA. It contains the highlights of the path which America'slaws are going and discusses the standards of keeping the air clean,controlling water pollution, controlling toxic substances, occupationalsafety. Criteria are significant risk, cost/benefit analysis, cost/effectivenessanalysis. Furthermore the article shows methods and competences, especiallycriteria setting, reformation discussion about separating the decision-makingprocess and control by courts. (orig./HSCH).</TEXT></DOC>